{"tid":2145921,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大freshman bb覺得讀書好chur? 十葉過來人分享經驗","createTime":"2020-08-08T09:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T07:29:19.000Z","uid":225931,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"faf940639defe29b60e5422ceaf02dcc1e7dbd29","tid":2145921,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"我第一年都好似你咁諗<br />\n後尾讀讀下又覺得唔錯，其實日常功課你有source係手基本上問題唔大<br />\n讀書係chur係辛苦, 但係都未至於話讀到想死,反而因爲身邊有一班朋友陪你讀溫書都溫得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家有咩唔明就拎出黎研究，再唔明就衝上office問prof, 成班十幾個人圍住個dept 門口都幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n運動活動方面其實想玩既都有，不過係規模細啲同無咁多奇怪既學會，不過呢樣就見人見智啦，但係你會遇到好多international student (唔係nds) 可以話叫做另一番體驗<br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得咁先係大學生活, 可能大家既追求唔同啦<br />\n我見到我啲中學同學去左其他u, 又通宵玩又post晒ig相咁,無錯係日日玩得好開心, 但係其實4年好快過, 你依加玩畢業就要還（唔計父幹撚), 慢慢思想上諗既野都開始唔同<br />\n<br />\n科大當然有好多差既野 (eg 同學普遍政治冷感 垃圾su 垃圾交通 唔重視人文社科 etc ） 但係都無改我覺得科大同其他u 唔同, 名氣唔差過香港一大, 我上年歐洲exchange, 出面啲人係知到科大個名, 甚至上堂同prof 吹水原來佢係去過科大交流, 有啲人讀master 因為收唔到科大offer 但係 收到一大offer 唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 唔係吹水，條友諗住讀CS)<br />\n<br />\n都係個句，想讀書想提升自己既人去科大讀係一個好好既選擇，其他就不了"},{"pid":"a3748865272f82826f4ff3628f80b6bb64d6b287","tid":2145921,"uid":312363,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"科大收分咁高點讀呀"},{"pid":"9f53e61ec22fd194d497d22447c4fc63e7463885","tid":2145921,"uid":38904,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"其實日常功課你有source係手基本上問題唔大<br />\n<br />\n你讀間U有汁都問題唔大架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b6c02274f4ad09e65d8df8cb5f44eae9dd3fbe","tid":2145921,"uid":300819,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:27:16.000Z","msg":"科大啲汁⋯⋯質素有啲參差<br />\n科大最on9嘅其實係grading <br />\n要我勤力唔緊要 入得嚟預咗chur<br />\n但chur到above mean都可以比C＋<br />\n呢下先痛苦<br />\n簡而言之 科大N展我屌你老母"},{"pid":"0f4b83bbe0f809fbfc3e7d2c722ca66831646f3e","tid":2145921,"uid":363481,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deac36b9181415f57814165244d33e5e2e6b956d","tid":2145921,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"29a21cf9db360cb0a13a578449b1dc95b0da2329","tid":2145921,"uid":112390,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\nnonju有自己嘅難處同彩數 <br />\n<br />\n如有得揀dse直入 邊個唔想<br />\n我都有努力過 我都試過每日訓4個鐘咁去溫書 操pp<br />\n咁我唔得即係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人鍾意男人 有人鍾意女人<br />\n各有取向<br />\n<br />\n有人適合DSE高壓模式一試定生死<br />\n有人適合HD/Asso持續考核GPA計分<br />\n各有自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n啲人覺得DSE考得差就一定係讀唔到書？一定唔應該入大學？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就真係勸啲人睇多啲書 唔好坐井觀天、活在自己嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n同埋nonju入hku唔令我覺得羞恥 亦唔係後門狗 nonju入hku係光明正大寫喺hku個website<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係啲人覺得只有DSE jupas先係光明正大入HKU嘅唯一選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lmao <br />\n<br />\nnonju都用自己努力考gpa 一步一步升上去 <br />\n（定係你覺得讀嘅hd/asso畀完錢就乜都唔洗理gpa自己就會好似啲警察受武肺感染人數咁自動升升升）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係畀錢 唔係靠關係 光明正大咁用非DSE嘅方式入HKU 我就真係唔知啲人憑乜嘢講nonju係走後門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實對比返我自己讀中學嘅經驗<br />\n讀完hd/asso嘅人 比起freshgrade嘅中學生<br />\n某程度上佢哋有更多嘅經驗喺接受全英嘅教學、寫paper &amp;reference （apa format）、group work合作、使用learn portal、應對freerider、睇百幾頁嘅ppt etc.（有錯望諒）<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然起點唔一樣 但最終都係為左讀大學 增長自己知識和技能 更好地融如社會 <br />\n未步入社會工作就已經要開始批鬥 分門別類 去區分前門後門 真係值得驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而至於hall收唔收我 唔到我話 <br />\n咁我禮拜一就打去admission office問下nonju嘅學生入唔入到hku 嘅hall<br />\n<br />\n而你用你認知嘅HKU hall文化覺得佢哋未必收我<br />\n<br />\n抑或可能係你坐井觀天呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後同宜家讀緊hd/asso嘅人講聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你來年過3爆4入到U"},{"pid":"0a113ceaee806949f3ff4efdfdc2b696f93b780c","tid":2145921,"uid":2607,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"同學普遍政治冷感 垃圾su<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年科大su係最高質最本土"},{"pid":"1d6a9090da5961c1458c511b8a1912dbe9a41860","tid":2145921,"uid":302503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"讀左成年科大，都冇乜歸屬感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps下年yr2"},{"pid":"bc5b9b068bcdae54a3cfdd8769546db3e0efbdef","tid":2145921,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a21cf9db360cb0a13a578449b1dc95b0da2329","tid":2145921,"uid":112390,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\nnonju有自己嘅難處同彩數 <br />\n<br />\n如有得揀dse直入 邊個唔想<br />\n我都有努力過 我都試過每日訓4個鐘咁去溫書 操pp<br />\n咁我唔得即係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人鍾意男人 有人鍾意女人<br />\n各有取向<br />\n<br />\n有人適合DSE高壓模式一試定生死<br />\n有人適合HD/Asso持續考核GPA計分<br />\n各有自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n啲人覺得DSE考得差就一定係讀唔到書？一定唔應該入大學？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就真係勸啲人睇多啲書 唔好坐井觀天、活在自己嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n同埋nonju入hku唔令我覺得羞恥 亦唔係後門狗 nonju入hku係光明正大寫喺hku個website<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係啲人覺得只有DSE jupas先係光明正大入HKU嘅唯一選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lmao <br />\n<br />\nnonju都用自己努力考gpa 一步一步升上去 <br />\n（定係你覺得讀嘅hd/asso畀完錢就乜都唔洗理gpa自己就會好似啲警察受武肺感染人數咁自動升升升）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係畀錢 唔係靠關係 光明正大咁用非DSE嘅方式入HKU 我就真係唔知啲人憑乜嘢講nonju係走後門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實對比返我自己讀中學嘅經驗<br />\n讀完hd/asso嘅人 比起freshgrade嘅中學生<br />\n某程度上佢哋有更多嘅經驗喺接受全英嘅教學、寫paper &amp;reference （apa format）、group work合作、使用learn portal、應對freerider、睇百幾頁嘅ppt etc.（有錯望諒）<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然起點唔一樣 但最終都係為左讀大學 增長自己知識和技能 更好地融如社會 <br />\n未步入社會工作就已經要開始批鬥 分門別類 去區分前門後門 真係值得驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而至於hall收唔收我 唔到我話 <br />\n咁我禮拜一就打去admission office問下nonju嘅學生入唔入到hku 嘅hall<br />\n<br />\n而你用你認知嘅HKU hall文化覺得佢哋未必收我<br />\n<br />\n抑或可能係你坐井觀天呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後同宜家讀緊hd/asso嘅人講聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你來年過3爆4入到U"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:13:29.000Z","msg":"睇嚟你真係好自卑，打一大篇嘢嚟講到自己好自豪咁，其實其他人依然當你係次一等嘅後門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0594303a167b4109bf473f8c208273f135632d13","tid":2145921,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f4b83bbe0f809fbfc3e7d2c722ca66831646f3e","tid":2145921,"uid":363481,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a3748865272f82826f4ff3628f80b6bb64d6b287","tid":2145921,"uid":312363,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"科大收分咁高點讀呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">已完全封鎖</span></span> 職訓局紅磡區分校"},{"pid":"50c69ba61258cf7ec14b230fb0056ff012ae5bd7","tid":2145921,"uid":363481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"797f8783ad69778fdd5ae7f10a518a53d50acf0c","tid":2145921,"uid":201890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"引戰po。<br />\n<br />\nHKU CU既一定就係好hea，日日玩通宵？<br />\n<br />\n科大就冇hea既同學？我大把科大既朋友又咪日日玩通宵，成績仲可以keep到添。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到好似入科大全部都係勤力既人<br />\n<br />\n入其他大學就冇勤力既人咁。"},{"pid":"a57434fae634645a85dbf2f6b50fb00678135ab9","tid":2145921,"uid":86449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d6a9090da5961c1458c511b8a1912dbe9a41860","tid":2145921,"uid":302503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"讀左成年科大，都冇乜歸屬感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps下年yr2"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"識D人讀完三年都冇乜歸屬感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 old seafood, 果陣讀三年"},{"pid":"0652debbb7cdaaa2293b5cd02d43f70d8985859e","tid":2145921,"uid":188396,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"797f8783ad69778fdd5ae7f10a518a53d50acf0c","tid":2145921,"uid":201890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"引戰po。<br />\n<br />\nHKU CU既一定就係好hea，日日玩通宵？<br />\n<br />\n科大就冇hea既同學？我大把科大既朋友又咪日日玩通宵，成績仲可以keep到添。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到好似入科大全部都係勤力既人<br />\n<br />\n入其他大學就冇勤力既人咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"科大chur=其喺大學唔chur??<br />\n間間大學都有既定印象㗎啦<br />\nHKU abc  落老蘭<br />\n中大村姑 書院<br />\n科大毒撚 讀書<br />\n唔通港大嘅印象係落club 落老蘭= 其他U冇人落club落老蘭?<br />\n而且六七成學生科大學生都係讀science/engine 而呢啲科就比較chur/爛grade<br />\n咪所以睇落科大個個人都話chur囉<br />\n樓豬淨係話科大讀書比較chur 多同學一齊溫書<br />\n你就理解係港大中大冇人讀書冇人勸力<br />\n係咪操dse中文閱讀操到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b676bafdd47108f2b92e2c99fb4451702de608cc","tid":2145921,"uid":228139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"屌點解好似睇過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />篇野有冇十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c31421d098fbceefcee75d4c71c3b70ce5d80b4","tid":2145921,"uid":237838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc5b9b068bcdae54a3cfdd8769546db3e0efbdef","tid":2145921,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a21cf9db360cb0a13a578449b1dc95b0da2329","tid":2145921,"uid":112390,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\nnonju有自己嘅難處同彩數 <br />\n<br />\n如有得揀dse直入 邊個唔想<br />\n我都有努力過 我都試過每日訓4個鐘咁去溫書 操pp<br />\n咁我唔得即係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人鍾意男人 有人鍾意女人<br />\n各有取向<br />\n<br />\n有人適合DSE高壓模式一試定生死<br />\n有人適合HD/Asso持續考核GPA計分<br />\n各有自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n啲人覺得DSE考得差就一定係讀唔到書？一定唔應該入大學？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就真係勸啲人睇多啲書 唔好坐井觀天、活在自己嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n同埋nonju入hku唔令我覺得羞恥 亦唔係後門狗 nonju入hku係光明正大寫喺hku個website<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係啲人覺得只有DSE jupas先係光明正大入HKU嘅唯一選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lmao <br />\n<br />\nnonju都用自己努力考gpa 一步一步升上去 <br />\n（定係你覺得讀嘅hd/asso畀完錢就乜都唔洗理gpa自己就會好似啲警察受武肺感染人數咁自動升升升）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係畀錢 唔係靠關係 光明正大咁用非DSE嘅方式入HKU 我就真係唔知啲人憑乜嘢講nonju係走後門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實對比返我自己讀中學嘅經驗<br />\n讀完hd/asso嘅人 比起freshgrade嘅中學生<br />\n某程度上佢哋有更多嘅經驗喺接受全英嘅教學、寫paper &amp;reference （apa format）、group work合作、使用learn portal、應對freerider、睇百幾頁嘅ppt etc.（有錯望諒）<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然起點唔一樣 但最終都係為左讀大學 增長自己知識和技能 更好地融如社會 <br />\n未步入社會工作就已經要開始批鬥 分門別類 去區分前門後門 真係值得驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而至於hall收唔收我 唔到我話 <br />\n咁我禮拜一就打去admission office問下nonju嘅學生入唔入到hku 嘅hall<br />\n<br />\n而你用你認知嘅HKU hall文化覺得佢哋未必收我<br />\n<br />\n抑或可能係你坐井觀天呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後同宜家讀緊hd/asso嘅人講聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你來年過3爆4入到U"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:13:29.000Z","msg":"睇嚟你真係好自卑，打一大篇嘢嚟講到自己好自豪咁，其實其他人依然當你係次一等嘅後門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd73aa846bd61635725ab3f1186efbbec60d09e","tid":2145921,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"少林寺 冇ulife<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀其他U好過"},{"pid":"cfe9b665848209bfffa206fe938eb97b952c2624","tid":2145921,"uid":246198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"科大交通算係OOKK 如果你坑口個邊上 小巴都叫好密既<br />\n大西北荃灣方向過黎就有D麻煩 車程比較長"},{"pid":"135fc060a838d7ea40c2bccf62e2c8372ca7b57d","tid":2145921,"uid":327173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe9b665848209bfffa206fe938eb97b952c2624","tid":2145921,"uid":246198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"科大交通算係OOKK 如果你坑口個邊上 小巴都叫好密既<br />\n大西北荃灣方向過黎就有D麻煩 車程比較長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"至弊清水灣道有TA就會塞到pk<br />\n到時就行路把la"},{"pid":"b01ee1ec7312415b2e001a1166a815ffe9161c3b","tid":2145921,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"科大本身都已經冇ulife<br />\n依家仲要毒喺屋企上堂<br />\n利申: 現役科大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog